title: Songs from Lift-off
creator_credit: Steve Steve Jodrell, Patricia Edgar and Australian Children's Television Foundation
brief_description: This video contains a collection of songs from the children’s series Lift off, including “The Lift off ” (series theme song), “Into the unknown”, “Lost”, “Do you remember?”, “Which one?”, “Bonza jingle”. All the favourite Lift off characters appear in the collection.
